Package: PrintSchedule
Title: Print Work Schedules from Shared Calendar Files
Version: 26.4.6
Authors@R:
    person("Andreas Gammelgaard", "Damsbo", email = "andreas@gdamsbo.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7559-1154"))
Description: A Shiny application for generating printable calendars from shared .ics calendar files (iCal format). Designed for healthcare workers to print work schedules from MyPlan shared calendar links. Features include color-coded event types, week and month views, and PDF export.
